if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8938206f446e8881fc58993c04b08f172ad6a82a","tid":82800,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係<br />\n利申：診所醫生</blockquote><br />\n冒充醫生可判囚三年<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】身兼執業律師的立法會議員涂謹申表示，根據本港法例，在外地註冊的律師或醫生，若他們以其專業身份在港作見證表面上看來可能違法；若他們非執業者而故意令人相信他們是執業者，即使沒有從事相關工作則屬違法。<br />\n醫務委員會發言人則稱，在外地註冊的醫生是不受該會監管的；但擅稱醫生屬違法，若有證據可被檢控。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20060331/5787815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20060331%2F5787815&d=AHA%2FaJVS9cdIgYgF0ZhJUksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=a3331566\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20060331%2F5787815&h=5b8ba0f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20060331/5787815</a><br />\n<br />\n默示資格也屬違法<br />\n根據香港法例第一百五十九章《法律執業者條例》第四十六條，任何人並非已註冊律師、大律師或外地律師的僱員，而故意冒充是上述僱員，又或採用任何名銜、加稱或說明以默示他是上述僱員者，即屬犯罪。<br />\n香港法例第一百六十一章《醫生註冊條例》第二十八條指出，任何人故意充作或採用任何稱號、名銜、加稱或說明，以默示其有資格從事內科或外科執業、已經註冊或姓名已經列入專科醫生名冊，又或自稱從事內科或外科執業或公布其姓名為執業者，即屬犯罪，一經定罪可被處第六級罰款及監禁三年。"},{"pid":"ce76db094ea299e6bca47833d0f38779bdb5a071","tid":82800,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:52:08.000Z","msg":"不少私家珍所啲護士妹都係mk來的<br />\n識有一間佢老婆坐陣<br />\n又點溝mk妹呀"},{"pid":"55396a6337d706310ca4eb6990e425c4d201accf","tid":82800,"uid":10844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:54:44.000Z","msg":"係診所𥄫緊護士再見到呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0526e357c682b5971a2b48070a8274fafdfe911e","tid":82800,"uid":57062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:57:07.000Z","msg":"牙醫麻醉左病人同護士搞咩真係冇人知"},{"pid":"f638e949607bfc446fcc60ee8370f64cd9f2c679","tid":82800,"uid":56194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>醒起之前睇個牙醫， 果到有3個護士， 一個醫生老婆， 一個靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一個普通人<br />\n<br />\n次次睇親， 個醫生講咩， 個老婆都串勁佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇佢個款， 我估佢食唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好地地做乜叫個老婆落舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n覺得佢好慘， 上次睇牙果時， <br />\n牙醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 拎個all ring(好似係， 申利：聽唔明)比我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：拿(又遞樣野比佢)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拎all ring 呀, 你拎咩呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 得la, 你係醫生呀ma<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n申利：訓係到完全唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bce14e1d4ccd215d668f20b4491c0db138cb3c7","tid":82800,"uid":27601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:59:45.000Z","msg":"男姑娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779888353734e53a5a21dd4e1f2259257d0756f7","tid":82800,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係<br />\n利申：診所醫生</blockquote><br />\n冒充醫生可判囚三年<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】身兼執業律師的立法會議員涂謹申表示，根據本港法例，在外地註冊的律師或醫生，若他們以其專業身份在港作見證表面上看來可能違法；若他們非執業者而故意令人相信他們是執業者，即使沒有從事相關工作則屬違法。<br />\n醫務委員會發言人則稱，在外地註冊的醫生是不受該會監管的；但擅稱醫生屬違法，若有證據可被檢控。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20060331/5787815\" data-sr-url=\"https://